    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classDali_1_1SignalDelegate" kindref="compound">SignalDelegate</ref> object allows direct connection to a signal that has been pre-configured internally. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>EG: The <ref refid="classDali_1_1SignalDelegate" kindref="compound">SignalDelegate</ref> can be created internally and exposed to the application-developer. They can then call the connect function to transparently bind to their callback. </para>
